text: "Mandinka" is a 1987 song by Irish singer Sinéad O'Connor and is the second single from her debut studio album The Lion and the Cobra. It went to number 17 in the United Kingdom, number 18 in New Zealand, number 6 in Ireland, number 39 in Australia, number 33 in Canada and number 24 in the Netherlands. ==References== Category:1987 songs Category:Indie rock songs Category:Sinéad O'Connor songs Category:Foo Fighters songs Category:Alanis Morissette songs
